Key Match Events: Sean Murphy's infield ground ball with the bases loaded scored a sliding Eli White in the 11th inning

Matt Olson then lofted a long fly ball to left, easily scoring White for the sacrifice fly that tied it

Adam Duvall then reached on an error by Blue Jays third baseman Addison Barger, whose throw sailed wide to first and scored Harris to tie the game
